"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty2.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{A Level I Specialty card, belonging to Deemer the Warlock. It uses \\svg{empower}, but does NOT belong to any School of Magic, despite the imagery.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.66\\linewidth]{translations/assets/de/specialty2.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{Sonderfähigkeit Stufe I von Hexer Deemer. Sie benötigt \\svg{empower}, zählt aber trotz des grafischen Designs NICHT zur Erdmagie-Schule.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:364
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Artifact}{\\subheader{Artifact Cards}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Artifact}{\\subheader{Artefakte}}\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:371
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Artifact cards\\index{Artifact cards} have a top and bottom effect. When you play one, you must \\textbf{choose which effect} you are using.\n"
"They are divided into 3 Levels: Minor, Major, and Relic, with different border color.\n"
"These Levels relate to the overall Power of the card and may be referenced when resolving certain effects or during Scenario setup.\n"
"Otherwise, all Artifact cards are normally shuffled together to form the Artifact Deck regardless of their Level.\n"
"They are gained through map exploration.\\par\n"
"Artifacts can be \\pagelink{Trading}{traded} in Alliance and Cooperative Scenarios.\\par\n"
"\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
msgstr ""
"Artefaktkarten\\index{Artefaktkarte} haben einen oberen und einen unteren Effekt. Beim Ausspielen musst du \\textbf{den Effekt wählen}, den du nutzen willst.  Artefakte haben drei Seltenheitsstufen (erkennbar an der Rahmenfarbe): Gewöhnliche, seltene und Relikt-Artefakte.  Diese Stufen beziehen sich auf die Effektstärken der Karten und können für Effekte anderer Karten oder spezifische Szenarioregeln wichtig sein.  Regulär bilden alle Artefakte (unabhängig der Kategorie) das Artefakt-Deck.  Man erhält sie durch die Erkundungen auf der Abenteuerkarte.\\par Artefakte können in Allianz- oder kooperativen Szenarien \\pagelink{Trading}{gehandelt} werden.\n"
"\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:391
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\node (major) {\\includegraphics[width=0.6\\linewidth]{\\cards/artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{major}\n"
"    \\draw (0.2, 0.8) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.7, 0.4) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.9, 0.9) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.25, 0.2) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node [below=0pt of major.south] {\\imagecaption{Major Artifact}};\n"
"  \\node (relic) [right=0.05\\linewidth of major.south east, anchor=south west] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/relic_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{relic}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of relic.south] {\\imagecaption{Relic Artifact}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node (minor) [above=4em of relic.north] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/minor_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{minor}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of minor.south] {\\imagecaption{Minor Artifact}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:401
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\footnotesize\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{1.}] Name\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{2.}] Effect\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{3.}] Level\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{4.}] Flavor text\n"
"  \\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\footnotesize\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{1.}] Name\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{2.}] Effekt\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{3.}] Seltenheit\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{4.}] Hintergrundgeschichte\n"
"  \\end{itemize}"

#. type: center
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:408
msgid "{\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\art/diplomats_ring.png}}"
msgstr "{\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\art/diplomats_ring.png}}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:413
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Spell Scroll Cards}{\\subheader{Spell Scroll Cards}}\\index{Spell Scroll cards}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Spell Scroll Cards}{\\subheader{Zauberspruchrollen}}\\index{Zauberspruchrollenkarte}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:418
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"During setup shuffle 10 of the Spell Scroll cards into the Artifact Deck.\n"
"Set the remaining 10 cards aside to form a Spell Scroll Deck.\n"
"Some locations or Scenario effects may call for them later.\n"
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Mische während des Spielaufbaus 10 Zauberspruchrollen in das Artefakt-Deck.\n"
"Die übrigen 10 Karten bilden das Zauberspruchrollen-Deck.\n"
"Einige Orte oder Szenarien können darauf Bezug nehmen.\n"
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:428
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/spell_scroll.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"         \\imagecaption{Spell Scroll card}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/spell_scroll.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"         \\imagecaption{Zauberspruchrollen-Karte}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:434
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"When you gain a Spell Scroll, place it next to your Hero Board, take the 2 top cards from the Spell Deck and place them face-down on the Spell Scroll.\n"
"You can look at these Spells at any time and they don't count toward your Hand \\svg{hand} Limit.\n"
"You can only have 2 Spell Scrolls at a time.\n"
"If you gain a third one, draw the new Spells normally and then decide whether to discard the newly gained Spell Scroll or replace one you already have (including all Spells on it).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"Erhältst du eine Zauberspruchrolle, platziere sie neben deinem Heldentableau. Ziehe 2 Karten vom Zauber-Deck und platziere sie verdeckt auf der Zauberspruchrolle.\n"
"Du darfst diese Zauber jederzeit ansehen. Sie zählen nicht zum Handkartenlimit \\svg{hand}.\n"
"Du darfst höchstens 2 Zauberspruchrollen zeitgleich besitzen.\n"
"Ziehst du eine dritte, ziehe die 2 Zauber wie üblich und entscheide dann, welche der drei Zauberspruchrollen (inklusive ihrer Zauber) du abwirfst.\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:444
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can play Spells from a Spell Scroll like any other Spell with the following exceptions:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item They don't count towards your Spell Limit.\n"
"    You can also play a Spell from your hand during this Combat Round.\n"
"    \\item You may use the Spell's \\textbf{lowest Power} \\svg{empower} \\textbf{effect}, without needing to pay its cost (e.g. in case of \\wikilink{spells/implosion}{Implosion} the cost is 1).\n"
"      You can't Empower the Spell with \\svg{empower} from any source.\n"
"\\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"Du kannst Zauber auf einer Zauberspruchrolle wie andere Zauber ausspielen, aber mit folgenden Ausnahmen:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item Sie zählen nicht zum Zauberlimit.\n"
"    Du kannst in dieser Kampfrunde auch einen Zauber von der Hand spielen.\n"
"    \\item Du darfst nur den niedrigsten \\svg{empower}-Effekt des Zaubers nutzen, musst aber auch keine Kosten zahlen (z. B. bei \\wikilink{spells/Implosion}{Implosion}). \n"
"    Du kannst den Zauber aus keiner Quelle durch \\svg{empower} verstärken.\n"
"\\end{itemize}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:453
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item They can't be used to increase the \\svg{empower} of another Spell.\n"
"    \\item You can \\pagelink{selling Spell Scrolls}{sell Spell Scrolls} at a Trading Post for 2 \\svg{gold} per each Spell on it.\n"
"      This works in addition to other effect of visiting the Trading Post.\n"
"    \\item After using or selling those Spells, the Spell card is \\textbf{removed}, not discarded.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item Du kannst andere Zauber nicht durch \\svg{empower} dieses Zaubers verstärken.\n"
"    \\item Du kannst diese Zauber für 2 \\svg{gold} pro Zauber \\pagelink{selling Spell Scrolls}{im Handelsposten verkaufen}. \n"
"      Dies gilt zusätzlich zum normalen Effekt des Handelspostens.\n"
"    \\item Nach der Nutzung oder dem Verkauf eines dieser Zaubers, \\textbf{entferne} ihn statt ihn abzuwerfen.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:455
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If the last Spell on a Spell Scroll is used or sold, place the Spell Scroll back in its Deck.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Wurde der letzte Zauber einer Zauberspruchrolle entfernt, lege sie zurück in ihr Deck.\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:458
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\medskip\n"
"Spell Scrolls are not part of your Deck, therefore they are not carried over between Scenarios in a Campaign."
msgstr ""
"\\medskip\n"
"Zauberspruchrollen sind nicht Teil deines Decks."

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:463
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{rampart,cove}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{War Machines}{\\subheader{War Machine Cards}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{rampart,cove}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{War Machines}{\\subheader{Kriegsmaschinen}}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:467
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  War Machines\\index{War Machine cards} are permanent cards that can be bought at either a \\pagelink{Trading Post}{Trading Post} or a \\pagelink{War Machine Factory}{War Machine Factory}.\n"
"  If you buy one at the Trading Post, \\textbf{you cannot use} any of the other normal functions of that Field during that visit.\n"
"  War machines are also more expensive at the Trading Post.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Kriegsmaschinen\\index{Kriegsmaschinenkarte} sind bleibende Karten, die im \\pagelink{Trading Post}{Handelsposten} oder der \\pagelink{War Machine Factory}{Kriegsmaschinenfabrik} gekauft werden können.\n"
"Kaufst du eine Kriegsmaschine im Handelsposten, kannst du \\textbf{keinen der anderen} Effekte des Handelspostens nutzen\n"
"und es gelten die teureren Kosten.\n"
"\n"

